snippet.title: CLICKOLDING - ANNOUNCEMENT TRAILER
snippet.description:
The man in the corner of your hotel room wants you to click something. He wants to watch you click it. CLICKOLDING is a dark incremental narrative game from Strange Scaffold, the developers of El Paso, Elsewhere, I Am Your Beast, and Space Warlord Organ Trading Simulator.

STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3011440/
PATREON: https://www.patreon.com/StrangeScaffold
DISCORD: https://discordapp.com/invite/YySjWvM
TWITCH: https://twitch.tv/WritNelson
TWITTER: https://twitter.com/StrangeScaffold
